text.section:
The depository shall:
Be established and maintained in each county and the City of Baltimore as a document file separate from the land records of the county or City;
Contain a record of the names of all homeowners associations for each county and the City of Baltimore;
Contain all disclosures deposited by a homeowners association; and
Be available to the public for viewing and for obtaining copies during the regular business hours of the office of the clerk.
